{"tid":1701284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有藍法官可以點？推上國際！","createTime":"2019-11-09T03:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:33:17.000Z","uid":215953,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea30afdba507a8ad2eae8c4168115b2b2f0273f3","tid":1701284,"uid":215953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:25:59.000Z","msg":"國際法院-海牙法庭<br />\n聯合國的司法機關<br />\n<br />\n上網睇佢只係處理主權國家間的爭端<br />\n只係講「香港警方有違人權」應該推唔到<br />\n<br />\n但如果美國進一步干涉<br />\n變成「美國因香港警方有違人權而推行法律制裁」<br />\n由美方控訴香港警方得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪要聯絡美國議員提出控訴?<br />\n定係由我地告上去？<br />\n<br />\n唔可以再俾黑警無法無天<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c56ed67e45a442fa89f4a52824f6d463bc8e5be","tid":1701284,"uid":94344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzEys6n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzEys6n.jpg&h=b894ae3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc637e0bcdce3517c3e0e9c40e9bd42e4df2381c","tid":1701284,"uid":143355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:35:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a7bb42e4847a66b3a4f3c596c06ad51b42d3ad","tid":1701284,"uid":215953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"a9dafb4b5a52d35f139dcee75b826e23159a6aa2","tid":1701284,"uid":215953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"4b2f268df31420d374f356b99ce4f2a7d39e2115","tid":1701284,"uid":215953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:36:01.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"24ae78a4bd9eb37d799b23866636b3646e3c4175","tid":1701284,"uid":215953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"07878